00:23:03,610 --> 00:23:04,580
hate you.

289
00:23:08,550 --> 00:23:09,920
Are you threatening me?

290
00:23:12,150 --> 00:23:13,120
No.

291
00:23:13,420 --> 00:23:15,260
I'm just telling the truth.

292
00:23:19,030 --> 00:23:21,360
You played weak before.

293
00:23:21,360 --> 00:23:22,000
Oh.

294
00:23:22,630 --> 00:23:23,830
I didn't.

295
00:23:24,800 --> 00:23:26,300
I haven't

296
00:23:26,300 --> 00:23:27,330
asked you about the emails yet.

297
00:23:27,800 --> 00:23:30,100
But if it can make Shu Yi happy,

298
00:23:30,570 --> 00:23:32,540
I wouldn't mind playing weak a few more times.

299
00:23:36,680 --> 00:23:38,450
You ungrateful creature!

300
00:23:38,450 --> 00:23:39,580
So you're

301
00:23:40,780 --> 00:23:41,950
admitting it?

302
00:23:48,620 --> 00:23:49,360
Dad.

303
00:23:51,560 --> 00:23:53,730
Don't call me that!

304
00:23:54,130 --> 00:23:55,130
I'm not admitting anything.

305
00:23:55,560 --> 00:23:57,360
Absolutely not!

306
00:23:59,870 --> 00:24:03,070
I know what happened to Hua Cing Technology.

307
00:24:03,840 --> 00:24:05,110
If it isn't handled properly,

308
00:24:05,710 --> 00:24:09,410
you won't stand any chance with Shu Yi.

309
00:24:12,610 --> 00:24:13,280
Thank you.

310
00:24:14,650 --> 00:24:16,280
I won't let you down.

311
00:24:23,220 --> 00:24:24,490
Shu Yi likes this.

312
00:24:40,670 --> 00:24:42,580
I've finished adjusting the table. It's fine.

313
00:24:42,580 --> 00:24:43,480
Great.

314
00:24:43,880 --> 00:24:44,480
How about you, Lin?

315
00:24:44,780 --> 00:24:45,750
All done.

316
00:24:45,750 --> 00:24:46,710
Lu?

317
00:24:46,710 --> 00:24:47,780
No problem.

318
00:24:47,780 --> 00:24:48,580
Yi Mian?

319
00:24:48,580 --> 00:24:49,820
That's about it. No problem.

320
00:24:51,920 --> 00:24:54,690
I want to thank you all for your support.

321
00:24:55,190 --> 00:24:56,790
We've finally finished Alpha in time,

322
00:24:57,590 --> 00:24:59,290
including the most difficult part,
program integration.

323
00:25:00,130 --> 00:25:01,430
We are the best!

324
00:25:09,070 --> 00:25:09,800
The bonus will be paid next month

325
00:25:09,800 --> 00:25:12,310
along with your salary.

326
00:25:13,310 --> 00:25:15,040
Thank you for saving Hua Cing Technology.

327
00:25:19,250 --> 00:25:20,410
Cool.

328
00:25:21,580 --> 00:25:24,620
Bonus!

329
00:25:25,620 --> 00:25:26,550
To celebrate,

330
00:25:26,550 --> 00:25:27,420
I'll treat you to lunch!

331
00:25:27,650 --> 00:25:28,960
Really?

332
00:25:29,760 --> 00:25:30,460
Go.

333
00:25:30,760 --> 00:25:32,730
Great!

334
00:25:34,716 --> 00:25:54,770
(Hua Cing Technology)

335
00:26:00,542 --> 00:26:05,247
(Hua Cing Technology)

336
00:26:14,830 --> 00:26:16,000
Is it downloaded?

337
00:26:25,610 --> 00:26:26,680
Why are you doing this?

338
00:26:28,720 --> 00:26:29,820
I take you as one of us.

339
00:26:30,320 --> 00:26:31,750
Is it worth it?

340
00:26:39,130 --> 00:26:41,090
I really didn't think it would be Lin.

341
00:26:43,760 --> 00:26:44,700
Well.

342
00:26:45,430 --> 00:26:47,070
I knew it was her.

343
00:26:48,000 --> 00:26:49,040
Why didn't you tell us then?

344
00:26:49,400 --> 00:26:50,400
Yeah.

345
00:26:54,770 --> 00:26:55,640
Sir.

346
00:26:56,480 --> 00:26:57,410
Sorry.

347
00:26:58,580 --> 00:27:00,480
I'm sorry. We didn't know it.

348
00:27:00,880 --> 00:27:02,450
Sorry, it is our fault.

349
00:27:05,020 --> 00:27:07,050
I thought you said no downsizing.

350
00:27:07,920 --> 00:27:09,320
Why did she still do that?

351
00:27:10,260 --> 00:27:12,460
Maybe somebody paid good money.

352
00:27:13,460 --> 00:27:15,600
Money makes the mare go.

353
00:27:16,600 --> 00:27:17,500
Right.

354
00:27:20,970 --> 00:27:22,700
Bing Wei hasn't brought Yu Zhen Xuan back yet?

355
00:27:23,870 --> 00:27:25,170
I just contacted him.

356
00:27:25,170 --> 00:27:28,010
He said Yu Zhen Xuan didn't want to leave.

357
00:27:31,140 --> 00:27:32,810
Looks like we're gonna have to
call in reinforcements.

358
00:28:02,040 --> 00:28:02,840
Yu Zhen Xuan.

359
00:28:03,380 --> 00:28:04,740
The real culprit has been found

360
00:28:04,740 --> 00:28:05,950
yet you're still handcuffing yourself.

361
00:28:05,950 --> 00:28:07,510
It's considered interference
with public function.

362
00:28:07,510 --> 00:28:08,650
Sue me then.

363
00:28:11,690 --> 00:28:12,890
You can't keep doing this.

364
00:28:14,190 --> 00:28:15,220
Are you listening?

365
00:28:17,460 --> 00:28:18,090
Hello.

366
00:28:18,090 --> 00:28:18,860
May I help you?

367
00:28:18,860 --> 00:28:19,930
I'm looking for Yu Zhen Xuan.

368
00:28:20,490 --> 00:28:21,260
Mr. Liu.

369
00:28:21,260 --> 00:28:22,260
Someone is here for you.

370
00:28:26,300 --> 00:28:27,200
Please.

371
00:28:27,200 --> 00:28:28,540
Talk some sense into him.

372
00:28:28,540 --> 00:28:29,740
The police station is not a restaurant.

373
00:28:29,970 --> 00:28:31,600
You can't stay as long as you want.

374
00:28:31,600 --> 00:28:32,740
I understand.

375
00:28:32,740 --> 00:28:33,240
(Culprits area)
Sorry.

376
00:28:33,810 --> 00:28:34,310
Thank you.

377
00:28:53,760 --> 00:28:55,060
(Next episode)
My heart is empty.

378
00:28:55,060 --> 00:28:56,630
There's nothing in it.

379
00:28:56,630 --> 00:28:58,400
And nothing will be in there.

380
00:29:00,400 --> 00:29:01,570
Pei Shou Yi.

381
00:29:01,570 --> 00:29:03,200
Not even a little bit?

382
00:29:06,070 --> 00:29:07,110
Are you happy now?

383
00:29:11,560 --> 00:29:13,960
