384
00:29:14,330 --> 00:29:17,400
♪I put on my new sneakers♪

385
00:29:18,640 --> 00:29:21,200
♪The old pair was left behind you♪

386
00:29:21,640 --> 00:29:26,040
♪I chased after you with them on
until they were broken♪

387
00:29:26,980 --> 00:29:31,150
♪Later on, I have to bear to see
you display affection with others♪

388
00:29:31,380 --> 00:29:35,250
♪The words said out of impulse
always make me wonder♪

389
00:29:35,320 --> 00:29:41,420
♪Our youth left no trace but on a piece of paper♪

390
00:29:42,160 --> 00:29:46,300
♪You took with you the only
love letter I had ever written♪

391
00:29:46,460 --> 00:29:50,230
♪Quietly, you left the spot
I saved for you deep in my heart♪

392
00:29:51,000 --> 00:29:58,070
♪How come this heavy rain
